          "type": "text",
          "text": "USP_InvoiceEmailLogAdd",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to log email activities related to invoices in the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "InvoiceProviderEmailLog",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table. It records details such as the invoice ID, EFT number, email recipients, and success status. Additionally, it logs the operation's metadata and any exceptions encountered during execution into an application log via another stored procedure, "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "USP_AppLogCreate",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
